          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In a statement, Beckham said, “I was drawn to the company through their work restoring some of the most beautiful classic cars through upcycling and electrification. Lunaz represents the very best of British ingenuity in both technology and design.”",
